name: Used Cloth Collection
details: A dynamic website of Used Cloth Collection
Admin can control buyer and seller, seller can add their products for sell, buyer can buy their products
Each buyer, seller and admin has different route with different functionalities
Seller can advertise all available products in the home page
Admin can access all buyer and seller
Admin also can remove any buyer and seller
